uma.caosd.cvl.m2m

Class ATLEngine

  • java.lang.Object
    • uma.caosd.cvl.m2m.ATLEngine
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    M2MEngine

    public class ATLEngine
extends java.lang.Object
implements M2MEngine
    Model to Model (M2M) transformation engine implementation for the ATL transformation language. It provides support to compile and run ATL model transformations at runtime.
